narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Amazing class! Too bad Prof. Rawson is retiring...

It's an amazing course, and as an English major, I definitely recommend reading Eliot beyond The Waste Land. Students should take this course after being well versed in Shakespeare, Milton, Pope, and other famous poets.
